Package: PASBench
Type: Package
Title: benchmarking study of seven (PAS) tools for scRNA-seq analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: yaru
Maintainer: yaru <1099656126@qq.com>
Description: This package contains benchmarking analysis methods of seven 
             Pathway Activity Score (PAS) tools (Pagoda2, AUCell, Vision, 
             GSVA, ssGSEA, PLAGE and z-score). It provide filtering and 
             normalizing before PAS calculation. It also provide clustering
             and visualization after PAS calcualtion
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    RColorBrewer,
    ggplot2,
    Seurat,
    dplyr,
    monocle,
    shiny,
    AUCell,
    GSVA
Suggests:
    VISION,
    pagoda2,
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
